of the ground vibrate a
little bit, some of it will be

00:07:23.430 --> 00:07:25.862
transferred as sound, so the air particles

00:07:25.862 --> 00:07:29.142
moving through the air, and
a lot of it will be heat.

00:07:29.142 --> 00:07:31.282
